        "timestamp": "2018-02-21 18:49:51.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nIn order to meet onap guidelines, it's better to change instead to:\n\n    <rollingPolicy class=\"ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.SizeAndTimeBasedRollingPolicy\">\n        <fileNamePattern>${outputDirectory}/${outputFilename}.%d{yyyy-MM-dd}.%i.log.zip</fileNamePattern>\n        <maxFileSize>50MB</maxFileSize>\n        <maxHistory>30</maxHistory>\n        <totalSizeCap>10GB</totalSizeCap>\n    </rollingPolicy>\n\nper https://wiki.onap.org/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=20087036",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
